- Hit and run.

31:41.180 --> 31:42.390
You're crazy.

31:42.550 --> 31:45.430
This place could be a gold mine.
We gotta at least check it out.

31:45.600 --> 31:48.350
This is exactly what we're trying
to get away from. Look what...

31:48.520 --> 31:52.150
- Stephen.
