Just don't panic, okay?

32:39.990 --> 32:41.490
Here.

33:16.980 --> 33:18.020
Keys to the kingdom.

33:18.940 --> 33:20.360
Grab the walkie-talkies.

33:30.410 --> 33:31.790
Fifteen upper and lower,

33:32.830 --> 33:33.830
Right here.

33:34.000 --> 33:35.630
How about a little music?

