33:43.130 --> 33:46.090
Hit them all. Might as well
have power in everything.

33:46.260 --> 33:47.800
We might need it.

34:13.659 --> 34:15.830
Jesus Christ.

34:16.000 --> 34:18.380
Stephen? Stephen.

35:12.220 --> 35:13.760
What do you think,
bag it or try for it?

35:13.930 --> 35:15.730
- You game?
