53:45.170 --> 53:48.420
<i>The Southern Hotel
and Motel Association of America...</i>

53:48.590 --> 53:51.340
<i>...today issued a strong denial
that troubles...</i>

53:51.510 --> 53:52.880
All your decisions made?

53:56.510 --> 53:58.100
Do you wanna abort it?

53:59.850 --> 54:01.270
Do you?

54:05.350 --> 54:07.520
Somebody better sit watch all the time.

54:07.690 --> 54:10.360
- They'll never get through there.
- Enough of them will.

54:10.530 --> 54:13.900
And it ain't just them things
we got to worry about.

54:14.070 --> 54:16.240
That chopper up there
could give us away...

54:16.410 --> 54:17.870
...if somebody comes messing around.

54:18.030 --> 54:20.620
What are they gonna do?
Land another pilot to fly it out?

54:20.790 --> 54:24.710
They're not gonna mess with a little bird
like that. They got enough on their hands.

54:24.870 --> 54:27.040
So I guess we forget about Canada,
right?

54:30.130 --> 54:31.880
Nobody cares about my vote, huh?

54:32.050 --> 54:34.380
Oh, come on, Fran.
I thought you were sleeping.

54:41.890 --> 54:44.390
Damn it, Fran.

54:51.940 --> 54:54.780
You were the one
that wanted to set up house.

55:01.450 --> 55:04.410
<i>The normal question,
the first question is always:</i>

55:04.580 --> 55:06.960
<i>Are these cannibals?
No, they are not cannibals.</i>

55:07.750 --> 55:09.670
<i>Cannibalism,
in the true sense of the word...</i>

55:10.210 --> 55:13.000
<i>...implies an intraspecies activity.</i>

55:13.170 --> 55:15.760
<i>These creatures
cannot be considered human.</i>

55:15.920 --> 55:17.260
<i>They prey on humans.</i>

55:18.090 --> 55:21.550
<i>They do not prey on each other.
That's the difference.</i>

55:21.720 --> 55:25.850
<i>They attack and they feed only
on warm human flesh.</i>

55:27.190 --> 55:31.770
<i>Intelligence?
Seemingly little or no reasoning power.</i>

55:31.940 --> 55:35.280
<i>What basic skills remain
are more remembered behaviors...</i>

55:35.440 --> 55:37.320
<i>...from, uh, normal life.</i>

55:39.450 --> 55:41.660
<i>There are reports
of these creatures using tools...</i>

55:41.830 --> 55:43.740
<i>...but even these actions
are the most primitive.</i>

55:43.910 --> 55:47.790
<i>The use of external articles
as bludgeons and so forth.</i>

55:47.960 --> 55:50.880
<i>I might point out to you
that even animals will adopt...</i>

55:51.040 --> 55:53.590
<i>...the basic use of tools in this manner.</i>

55:53.750 --> 56:00.050
<i>These creatures are nothing
but pure motorized instinct.</i>

56:00.220 --> 56:02.180
<i>We must not be lulled by the concept...</i>

56:02.350 --> 56:05.310
<i>...that these are our family members
