56:05.470 --> 56:09.020
<i>They are not.
They will not respond to such emotions.</i>

56:09.190 --> 56:14.730
<i>They are.
- They must be destroyed on sight.</i>

56:14.900 --> 56:16.900
Look, we need to block those entrances.

56:17.070 --> 56:20.490
Those trucks are the answer.
We put one at each door.

56:21.320 --> 56:25.160
<i>] They're working on
an analysis of this whole phenomenon...</i>

56:25.330 --> 56:27.330
<i>...uh, from the point of view
of a viral disease.</i>

56:27.500 --> 56:29.710
<i>They're doing various laboratory tests...</i>

56:29.870 --> 56:32.670
<i>...to see if they can deal with it
in that way.</i>

56:32.830 --> 56:37.170
<i>Perhaps come up with some kind
of a workable vaccine.</i>

56:37.840 --> 56:38.840
Hey, Fran.

56:39.010 --> 56:41.680
<i>According to this report,
the problem they've run into in Atlanta...</i>

56:41.840 --> 56:44.050
<i>...is that there are
no live specimens available.</i>

56:44.220 --> 56:47.390
<i>Uh, in that area, there are in fact...</i>

56:48.060 --> 56:51.520
<i>Uh, we've had a filmed report
shot in Atlanta.</i>

56:51.690 --> 56:54.520
<i>But it has not arrived yet.
Contact has been...</i>

56:54.690 --> 56:56.520
I would've made you all
coffee and breakfast...

56:56.690 --> 56:58.440
...but I don't have my pots and pans.

57:00.610 --> 57:02.360
<i>Also, uh...</i>

57:03.280 --> 57:05.370
<i>Wait a minute.
Uh, there's another report...</i>

57:05.530 --> 57:06.790
May I say something?

57:07.450 --> 57:08.910
Sure.

57:10.000 --> 57:11.540
Sorry you found out I'm pregnant...

57:11.710 --> 57:14.790
...because I don't wanna be treated
any differently than you treat each other,

57:14.960 --> 57:16.130
Oh, hey, Fran, come on.

57:16.290 --> 57:18.050
And I'm not gonna be
den mother for you guys.

57:19.210 --> 57:20.630
I wanna know what's going on.

57:21.050 --> 57:23.050
And I wanna have something to say
about the plans.

57:23.220 --> 57:24.260
There's four of us, okay?

57:24.430 --> 57:25.760
Jesus, Fran.

57:26.180 --> 57:28.100
Fair enough.

57:28.260 --> 57:29.600
Okay. Now, what's going on?

57:29.770 --> 57:33.100
We're going out.
And you're not coming with us.

57:33.270 --> 57:36.150
And you won't come with us
until you learn how to handle yourself.

57:39.400 --> 57:41.570
Something else.

57:42.610 --> 57:43.740
I don't know about you two...

57:43.910 --> 57:45.990
...but I wanna learn
how to fly that helicopter.

57:48.620 --> 57:52.080
If anything happens to you,
we have to be able to fly out of here.

57:53.580 --> 57:55.210
She's right, man.

57:57.380 --> 57:59.250
Come on, let's go.

58:01.170 --> 58:03.680
And I don't want you to leave me
without a gun again.

58:16.600 --> 58:19.610
I just might be able to figure out
how to use it.

58:22.110 --> 58:23.860
I'm sorry, Stephen.

58:24.610 --> 58:26.360
It's all right. It's all right.

58:26.820 --> 58:28.120
Stephen.

58:31.160 --> 58:32.500
Yeah?

58:33.790 --> 58:35.330
Be careful.

58:37.040 --> 58:38.130
Yeah, we'll be all right.

58:38.290 --> 58:41.340
<i>To at least keep
some of the chaos under control.</i>

58:41.500 --> 58:42.840
<i>Bowling for Dollars at 6.</i>

58:43.010 --> 58:44.670
<i>In spite of everything,
as you can hear...</i>

58:44.840 --> 58:46.800
<i>...there are still people
with a sense of humor.</i>

58:54.140 --> 58:55.140
How about it?

58:55.640 --> 58:56.730
Getting it.

59:08.160 --> 59:10.370
I'm not too sure of this thing.
I'll just ride pick-up.

59:10.530 --> 59:12.160
I grew up in one of these things.
Come on.

59:12.330 --> 59:13.330
All right.

59:47.530 --> 59:50.530
<i>Hey, Too Tall Too Slow Two, come in.</i>

59:51.030 --> 59:52.910
You look my size
when you're sitting in a truck.

59:56.040 --> 59:58.620
<i>What I wanna know is how we both
got in the same force together...</i>

59:58.790 --> 01:00:00.120
<i>...you being so large and all.</i>

