it was a midget force.

01:00:02.590 --> 01:00:04.210
<i>They needed somebody to look up to.</i>

01:00:05.590 --> 01:00:07.800
Hey, Where's fly boy? Where's his 20?

01:00:07.970 --> 01:00:11.590
